function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idSelf, 4)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSelf, S_FX_SPAWN)
	
	T_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "MONSTERS")

	for i, idMonster in ipairs(T_MONSTERS) do
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idMonster, true)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idActorDetector, 2)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorDetector, S_FX_SPAWN_02)
	
	for i, idFoliage in pairs(tFoliage) do
		Hydra.ActorSetCollidable(idFoliage, false)
	end
end

unk_993f312.value:
T_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "MONSTERS")

-- Initial Setup
for i, idMonster in ipairs(T_MONSTERS) do
	--Munchin on snax
	SNO_JOB_STATE_AI_STATE = Hydra.ReferenceAIState("GenericJobState");
	Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(Hydra.QuestGetOwner(), SNO_JOB_STATE_AI_STATE, idMonster, 0.0);
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idMonster, false)
end

unk_39af3bb.value:
--Backup to make monster targetable in case the quest completes or cleans up without triggering Set Targetable
T_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "MONSTERS")

for i, idMonster in ipairs(T_MONSTERS) do
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idMonster, true)
end
